10. CONCLUSION

The School Result Management System successfully demonstrates the implementation of CRUD operations using Java, JDBC, and MySQL. The project provides a practical understanding of database connectivity, object-oriented programming, and result management. It is a useful application for maintaining student academic records efficiently and accurately.
